Output artifacts/local-setup.gif

Set Shell powershell
Set Width 1400
Set Height 780
Set FontSize 18
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 18
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WaitTimeout 10s

Require python
Require npm
Require docker

Type "python --version"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "npm --version"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "docker compose version"
Enter
Sleep 2s
